text: Carmen Carrera (born April 13, 1985) is an American reality television personality, model, burlesque performer, and actress. She is known for appearing on the third season of the Logo reality television series RuPaul's Drag Race. Carrera is a transgender woman and a transgender rights activist. ==References== Category:1985 births Category:Living people Category:American movie actors Category:American television actors Category:LGBT models Category:LGBT actors Category:American LGBT rights activists Category:LGBT people from New Jersey Category:Models from New Jersey Category:Actors from New Jersey
